summary:
Make a difference with IT!!! for people üòÄ, profit üí∏ and most of all, the Planet üåç

We are Aliter Networks, proud B Corp and part of Circular IT group.
https://circularitgroup.com/fr/
https://www.aliternetworks.com/

We believe that the reuse of IT makes a difference. Therefore, we want to have 500.000 IT products reused by 2025.Yes it is possible üí™

Since 2009, we have avoided the production of over 400,000 kilograms of e-waste and reused over 196,000 network and server products with over 3,000 companies, data centers, banks, universities and hospitals etc. in 129 countries. 

Our state-of-the-art testing processes, extensive knowledge of critical IT infrastructure needs, and certified engineers help guarantee a significantly extended lifetime of network & server equipment, mostly from Cisco, HP, Dell and Juniper. As a B Corp, Aliter Networks balances purpose & profit and is recognized in using its business as a force for good. We take pride in helping our customers to use IT as a force for good.
From the Netherlands, we are working together towards our vision to have every company using sustainable technology by 2025.

A project? Let's talk: romuald.lagrange@aliternetworks.com
